            <ui uid="2" type="BodyText" width="300" height="200" x="center" y="200" margin="0" fontAlign="center" effect="none" time="1" trans="slideup" ease="QuintEaseOut" syncType="build">
              <bodyBullet id="bb1" timeIn="1" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[While your dealership may organize the customer experience into slightly different categories, chances are you still try to create satisfied and loyal customers in all areas.
And you know that it takes teamwork across all areas to really succeed.]]>
