              <actui uid="3" type="feedbacktext" width="710" height="80" x="center" y="bottom" margin="10" fontSize="14">
                <item type="correct" id="pos">
                  <![CDATA[Good job! You can see how each team member contributes to creating customer loyalty. The teamwork concept also applies to the connection between Sales and Service and Parts. Examples include Sales Consultants introducing customers to Service and Parts personnel and helping new owners set up their first service appointment. You depend on each other to deliver a consistently great experience!]]>
